"Damn it! Damn it! damn it! damn it!!" TK sweared, as the 2 stinger missiles 
just missed him. The 2 explosions sent TK flying, though.

"Gah!!" TK said as he hit the ground. He stood up, and looked at the other 
missile heading at him. He got an idea, and stood still. The missile got 
closer, and closer, and closer. He then jumped back, as the missile hit the 
ground, sending TK flying.
